<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.5">
<l>meṉṉaṭai yaṉṉam parantu viḷaiyāṭum villiput tūruṟai vāṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉaṭi kāṇpatō rācaiyi ṉāleṉ porukayaṟ kaṇṇiṇai tuñcā</l>
<l>iṉṉaṭi cilōṭu pālamu tūṭṭi yeṭuttaveṉ kōlak kiḷiyai</l>
<l>uṉṉoṭu tōḻamaik koḷvaṉ kuyilē yulakaḷan tāṉvarak kūvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My pair of carp[-like], warring eyes will not sleep out of the desire to see the golden feet</l>
<l rend="indent">of [the Lord] who resides in Villiputtūr,</l>
<l>where the soft-gaited hamsas spread around and play.</l>
<l>I will have my beautiful parakeet—which I brought up feeding nectarine milk</l>
<l rend="indent">along with sweet rice—befriend you, O koel!</l>
<l>Cry so that the [Lord] who measured the worlds comes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
